    "experimental_data": {
        "key_results": "All tablets met USP criteria for hardness (>15 kp), friability (<1%), and content uniformity (RSD <6%). The 086_C3 formulation (8% Carbopol) exhibited the most promising sustained release profile, following zero-order kinetics (r²=0.977) and extending release over 18 hours.",
        "statistical_analysis": "Dissolution profiles were compared using the f2 similarity factor. All formulations had f2 values <50 compared to the immediate-release reference, indicating dissimilar release profiles. Linear regression was used for kinetic modeling.",
